title: Outdoor NERF WAR 20 vs 20!!! Unboxing 60 guns + 4000 rounds of ammo
description:
We bought 60 nerf guns and 4000+ nerf darts and invited all our friends for an epic outdoor nerf battle. we also used the giant legos from our lego fishing cabin video. 

Check out some other great videos from the Outdoor Boys YouTube channel.
Lego Fishing Cabin https://youtu.be/EO7Q9rGfrE8
